<plot>The phrase "entertaining angels" refers to the practice of treating all guests--be they kings or peasants--as if they were visiting angels. This is the challenge for all humble Christians and the one Dorothy Day rises to meet.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?179258</url></doc>
